properties.name: Time Wall
properties.definition_text: a  small  object  moving  at  constant  velocity  passes behind  an  opaque  barrier.  The  task  is  to  estimate  the  moment  when  the  object will  reappear.  It  differs  from  a  number  of  other  time-estimate  tasks  in  that discrete  mediating  responses  such  as  counting  or  taping  are  of  no  direct obvious  aid.
